error.message: Value of core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 is not compatible with the next major version of Drupal core. See https://drupal.org/node/3070687.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to designate that the extension is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://drupal.org/node/3070687.
Parse error in composer.json. Having a composer.json is not a requirement in general, but if there is one, it should be valid. See https://drupal.org/node/2514612.
